(42, 6, 39, 40, 15, 14, 14, 'the blind lead the blind', 'Blind Leaders and Their Consequences', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of ''the blind lead the blind,'' illustrating the danger of misguided leadership. They highlight the inevitable downfall that occurs when those lacking insight guide others.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
